title: 25-sai no Joshikousei
synopsis: Once most students are done with high school, they leave and never come back. However, at 25 years old, Hana Natori  finds herself in the role of a student once more at her aunt's request.
related_anime: ['25-sai no Joshikousei: Kodomo ni wa Oshierarenai Koto Shiteyaru yo']
